## 12. Error Handling & Fallbacks

- If the Sheets API fetch fails (network error, invalid key, quota exceeded), the ad containers remain hidden. No error is displayed to the user (only a silent `console.warn`).
- If the API key environment variable is missing at build time, the generated pages will have an empty string for the key, and the fetch will fail (silently). The generator logs: `Warning: GOOGLE_SHEETS_API_KEY environment variable not set. Ads will not work.`
- If the spreadsheet does not contain the expected columns, the script will not render any ads and log a warning.

